{"tid":884643,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"刀劍神域VS倚天屠龍記?邊本好睇?","createTime":"2018-10-31T18:43:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T00:12:35.000Z","uid":14941,"like":53,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8946081ffb36bdab56789d37b38307d5c10eee7a","tid":884643,"uid":14941,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T18:43:40.000Z","msg":"刀劍神域<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倚天屠龍記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家都係鬥主角威能, 論劇情, 刀劍完勝, 除非張無忌識左手拎倚天劍, 右手屠龍刀, 叫金毛獅王幫佢撐十秒<br />\n<br />\n技能系統: 刀劍完勝,  心法系統根本隨佢亂UP, 一定係SAO HP/SP 量化有系統<br />\n<br />\n後宮: 大家都係一堆後宮, 刀劍桐人識分邊個係正妻, 邊個係妾; 張無忌就係度扭黎扭去, 成個女人咁唔肯表白,睇見都炆<br />\n<br />\n天分: 桐人同張無忌都係天才, 一個有最快反應時間, 一個有練武天份+九陽神功。但桐人識得用佢既能力去獲最大得益, 例如識用回復HP量&gt;被扣血量去串人, 同時慳力;  無雙刀技時又識用技能連發去CANCEL硬直, 相反張無忌又要扮廢, 發揮威能時又去唔盡,例如守光明頂時又扭黎扭去唔想完勝<br />\n<br />\n性格: 桐人識分輕重, 溝女時溝女, 打王時打王。相反張無忌成日扮野, 溝女時扮無溝, 身懷神功時死都唔用, 搶人把劍還返俾人, 救命, 張無忌真係好撚ON9!!"},{"pid":"b30bb88c40a416d21f1e64a308ac63a03f203e42","tid":884643,"uid":199590,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T19:57:07.000Z","msg":"最好睇係出包王女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f3f788aa5eb475d53d649963cd54e5252accccb","tid":884643,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T20:00:24.000Z","msg":"尋秦記"},{"pid":"b18fea3a07207c592d0e5201d080006b1d7dfa08","tid":884643,"uid":169468,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T20:26:35.000Z","msg":"粉俠傳"},{"pid":"0a65a287bef6b256951b5b91205cb6e8cc7cebd0","tid":884643,"uid":149494,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T22:51:33.000Z","msg":"刀劍神域高質好多<br />\n<br />\n講真，金庸d書麻麻"},{"pid":"c5ae1eeb7e48c2238cd458a5dc7133f2c5a5aa68","tid":884643,"uid":94551,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T23:22:31.000Z","msg":"6/10 冇是咁的"},{"pid":"9acdc4fba7123b2fa707f82ef93d16ed113bfd2b","tid":884643,"uid":98887,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-31T23:24:32.000Z","msg":"加速世界仲好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3c080abb5e0686dfe607f48c54cc15b62cb9e17","tid":884643,"uid":10925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:12:35.000Z","msg":"樓主個topic改一改。比緊主角only."}]}